.com/europe/?url=https://www.moneycontrol.com/news/business/cough-syrup-crisis-us-trade-heat-and-r-d-breakthroughs-define-indian-pharma-s-in-2025-13751696.html&classic=true","imageUrl":null,"pubDate":"2025-12-31T00:00:00","source":"Moneycontrol"},{"id":"251231122846829","title":"Wockhardt Ltd announces EMA grants accelerated assessment to WCK 5222.","summary":"Wockhardt Ltd announces EMA grants accelerated assessment to WCK 5222.","url":"https://www.marketscreener.com/news/wockhardt-says-ema-grants-accelerated-assessment-to-wck-5222-ce7e59d8dc8cf227","imageUrl":null,"pubDate":"2025-12-31T00:00:00","source":"MarketScreener"},{"id":"415246","title":"Indian Pharma stocks surged on Friday, with Nifty Pharma index gaining over 1% post US BIOSECURE Act inclusion in NDAA.\nWockhardt led gains (+6.5%), followed by Divi's, Laurus Labs, Aurobindo, and Biocon (2-3.5%). Macquarie prefers Divi's and Syngene.","summary":"Indian Pharma stocks surged on Friday, with Nifty Pharma index gaining over 1% post US BIOSECURE Act inclusion in NDAA.\nWockhardt led gains (+6.5%), followed by Divi's, Laurus Labs, Aurobindo, and Biocon (2-3.5%). Macquarie prefers Divi's and Syngene.","url":"https://www.cnbctv18.com/market/pharma-stocks-biggest-trigger-behind-surge-wockhardt-aurobindo-laurus-sai-life-piramal-share-price-us-biosecure-19796248.htm","imageUrl":null,"pubDate":"2025-12-19T09:52:51","source":"CNBC TV 18"},{"id":"413815","title":"Indian pharma exports hit $30B in FY25, with medicines reaching 200+ markets, including stringent ones like the US.\nKey players like Sun Pharma, Cipla, and Dr Reddy's drive exports, while Wockhardt gains USFDA NDA for Zaynich antibiotic.","summary":"Indian pharma exports hit $30B in FY25, with medicines reaching 200+ markets, including stringent ones like the US.\nKey players like Sun Pharma, Cipla, and Dr Reddy's drive exports, while Wockhardt gains USFDA NDA for Zaynich antibiotic.","url":"https://www.ndtvprofit.com/markets/indian-pharma-exports-hit-30-bil